==Aglam ==
Ard i-tt-nbaɛ wasif n wansifen seg idraren waṭlaṣ anammas, seg taɣzi n <math> 1800  m </math> f uflla n wakal, aggugen iɣbula ns f tamdint n [[Xnifra]] s <math> 40 Km</math>, aggugen daɣ  f iɣrem n [[Mrirt]] s <math> 26 Km</math>.

Asif nnaɣ seg iɣrem n Xnifra ifka yixf nns s umnid n [[iffus]], ilma yekcem s [[Azaɣar n tadla|uẓaɣar n Tadla]], ilma kcmend sers isaffen n Tasawt d Wad lxḍer d wasif n Wad lɛbid seg iẓẓelmḍ.

